SELECT COUNT(QGDS_ID) FROM tab_qgds qgds LEFT JOIN tab_qgd qgd ON qgd.QGD_BH = qgds.QGDS_MBH WHERE 1 = 1 AND qgds.QGDS_SSDWBH = '01' AND ((CONVERT(qgds.QGDS_WLSL,DECIMAL(19,3)) - (CONVERT(IFNULL(qgds.QGDS_CGWLSL,0),DECIMAL(19,3))) > 0 OR (CONVERT(IFNULL(qgds.QGDS_FZSL,0),DECIMAL(19,3)) - CONVERT(IFNULL(qgds.QGDS_CGFZSL,0),DECIMAL(19,3))) > 0 ) AND qgd.QGD_SHR IS NOT NULL AND qgd.QGD_TYR IS NULL
